    • createRequest

      static void createRequest(String senderID, String recipientID, RequestType_Enum requesttype, String requestdetail1, String requestdetail2)
      This method creates a request with the given parameters.
      Parameters:
      senderID - The ID of the user sending the request.
      recipientID - The ID of the user receiving the request.
      requesttype - The type of request being made.
      requestdetail1 - The first detail of the request.
      requestdetail2 - The second detail of the request.
